     ) in the domain C-terminus [
     <xref ref-type="bibr">
      19
     </xref>
     ], including residues from the Rev7 interaction site identified in this work. The residues 1201–1204 from H2–H3 loop and the beginning of H3, displaying large Δϖ' upon Rev7 binding, also belong to a region conserved among eukaryotes, except
     <em>
      S. cerevisiae
     </em>
     and related yeasts [
     <xref ref-type="bibr">
      19
     </xref>
     ].
    </p>
